data.description: Stunning Country property, situated on 2.2 acres minutes from Cannon AFB and Down Town Clovis. This 3 bedroom 2 bath home features two living areas, formal dining room, spacious bedrooms and baths. Primary suite boast's a walk in closet, dressing area and French doors to the back yard. Back acreage includes pipe fencing, 2 horse stall and tack room. Plenty of room for family, pets, livestock and toys.
